<i>noun</i>: 염라대왕 [염나대왕] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>염라대왕 [염나대왕]</dt><br>
<dd>Yama</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 죽은 사람이 살아 있을 때 한 일의 잘잘못을 심판하는 저승 세계의 왕.</dd><br>
<dd>The king of the underworld in Buddhism who judges the right and wrong of the actions a dead person did when he/she was alive.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>